@startuml RecruiterVerificationFlow
title 1.2.2 Recruiter Verification Flow

skinparam swimlaneWidth same
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam activityBorderColor #2F6FED
skinparam conditionStyle diamond
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8E1
skinparam noteBorderColor #D97706

|#LightBlue|Recruiter|
|#Lavender|System|
|#Wheat|Moderator|

|Recruiter|
start

:Step 1: Register recruiter account;
note right: POST /api/auth/register\nwith role = RECRUITER

:Step 2: Complete company profile;

|System|

while (Profile < 97%?) is (Yes)
  :Step 4 (If profile < 97%):\nList missing fields;

  |Recruiter|
  :Update profile fields;

  |System|
  :Step 3: Recalculate completeness;
endwhile (No)

:Create verification request\n(status = Pending);

|Moderator|
:Step 5: Review verification request;

if (Approve?) then (Approved)
  :Step 6 (If approved):\nIssue verified badge\nstatus = Verified;
else (Rejected)
  :Step 6 (If rejected):\nReject with reason\nstatus = Rejected;
endif

|System|
:Step 7: Notify Recruiter\nverification result;

stop

@enduml
